title: Purchase right to summon a second gotchi
body:
Let summoners pay 10,000 GHST to the shared Treasury and summon a second Gotchi from portals. 

This applies in cases where there are two extremely rare Gotchis in the same portal and it's a waste to let one never be summoned.
author: 0xAEC4075e4fc8cE829BC4f0cFD5e2fA10dd2b12D1
